run(sql="

select 
ag.parentCategory as categoryName,
ag.parentCategoryId as categoryId, 
count(DISTINCT ag.orderId) AS Total_Orders
FROM `last51Days(orderSuccessView)` ov
JOIN `last51Days(saleOrder)` so ON ov.orderId = so.orderCode 
JOIN `last51Days(suborder)` subo ON so.orderId = subo.orderId 
JOIN `last51Days(agCmDump)` ag on ag.subOrderCode = subo.subOrderCode where (ag.shippedStatus <> 'CLD' OR ag.shippedStatus IS NULL OR ag.shippedStatus='NA')
group by ag.parentCategory,ag.parentCategoryId

",rows=1000)

paragraphs.text:
run(sql="

with cte as(
        Select a.subOrderId as subo, ag.parentCategory, ag.parentCategoryId from `temp.final_attribution_` a
	    LEFT JOIN (select parentCategory, parentCategoryId, subOrderId, shippedStatus from `last51Days(agCmDump)`) ag 
	    on a.subOrderId = ag.subOrderId
	    where (ag.shippedStatus <> 'CLD' OR ag.shippedStatus IS NULL OR ag.shippedStatus='NA')
	    and (a.orderDate>='2023-02-01')
)

select cte.parentCategory as categoryName,
       cte.parentCategoryId as categoryId, 
       count(DISTINCT cte.subo) AS Total_Orders,
       sum(ue.nm) as total_nm
from cte left join `last51Days(unitEconomicsBaseTable)` ue
ON cte.subo=ue.subOrderId	
group by cte.parentCategory,cte.parentCategoryId
order by cte.parentCategory

",rows=1000)
